'''John Beyer''' is the author of a number of [[roleplaying game]] sourcebooks including ''[[Shadows of the Empire Planets Guide]]'', ''[[Heroes & Rogues]]'' and [[Operation: Elrood (book)|''Operation: Elrood'']]. He has also co-written two short stories with [[Wayne Humfleet]], "[[Swoop Gangs]]" and "[[Lumrunners]]" for the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]''.

{{Bio-stub}}

