===Short stories===
*{{Journal|6|Swoop Gangs}} (1995)
*{{Journal|9|Lumrunners}} (1996)

===Roleplaying-game sourcebooks===
*''[[Heroes & Rogues]]'' (1995)
*''[[Shadows of the Empire Planets Guide]]'' (1996)
*[[Operation: Elrood (book)|''Operation: Elrood'']] (1997)

